release_note: Babelnet uses Blockchain to increase security. New features added.
Babelnet uses Blockchain to increase security. New features added.
Babelnet uses Blockchain to increase security. Migration problem fixed.
Babelnet uses Blockchain to increase security.
You can now use babel as an encrypted storage for your own notes text notes images and even other files. Naturally synchronized across all your devices.
Now it is possible to delete messages and conversations across all your devices.
Now supports Mute for conversations. Muted conversations are completely silenced and they do not display any kind of notifications.
Chatting is now easier. Let the daily thoughts flow in the new Chat conversation that is always easy to find!
In message settings you can now enable automatic download of attachments right after receiving a message.
You can now manage all of your devices for each profile.

Attachment viewer added you can now browse and filter all attachments within the app through our new attachment viewer! Auto delete message optimization you can now download the attachment first and then open the message to start the countdown Enhanced Full text search
Now you can change your profile picture and remove contacts from your address book.
Some of our users said that our easy to navigate wizard was not easy to navigate enough. So we made it better. Please update the app to get the latest experience!

Babelnet brings you yet again new features to make your user experience even better. Introducing Babelnet business cards for easy addition of your friends colleagues into your Babelnet contact list. And for our Babelnet Pro users you now have the possibility to brand your Babelnet application with custom colours and logos.
Finally! The all new re designed Babelnet is here update your application now and enjoy a brand new design fresh look and improved user interface. And of course still as secure as ever!

Thank you for using Babel! We bring updates regularly to further improve your experience. Here s what s new: Possibility to search your conversations by contact name Refresh your contact list by simply swiping down Bug fixes

Big news! The next few months will see Babel undergoing a series of improvements including a brand new design change of icon and most importantly name: we will now be Babelnet. This version brings some initial minor changes but a lot more will be coming so stay tuned!

Thank you for using Babel! We bring updates regularly to further improve your experience.
